Rhoderick Ramos Santos (born October 10, 1982), more commonly known as simply Erik Santos, is a Filipino singer, occasional actor, TV host, commercial model, and the first Grand Champion of the ABS-CBN singing competition Star in a Million Season 1 in 2003.
Erik Santos was ABS-CBN's Star in a Million Grand Champion last January 2004.
His much-awaited debut album aptly titled "This Is The Moment" shows that Erik's moment has indeed come.
His much-awaited debut album aptly titled "This Is The Moment" shows that Erik's moment has indeed come.
His passion for music started during his childhood years.
His first single, Pagbigyang Muli, remained number one of WRR's hit chart for more than 20 weeks together with his other songs filling up the chart simultaneously.
Santos was born on October 10, 1982 in Malabon, Metro Manila, Philippines.
As soon as he won the singing competition Star in a Million in 2003, he temporarily stopped studying, because of his busy schedule.
He graduated in March 2010.
In 2003, Santos joined Star in a Million singing contest, and became part of the wildcard entry to the Final 10 of the show.
